{"tid":1865913,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"今日返工好威咁同女同事講我有幾箱酒\"精\"搓手液","createTime":"2020-02-06T12:21:07.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-06T13:47:23.000Z","uid":8968,"like":8,"dislike":21,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"8f388cbd197e576591adc2db60f4feaa607e3172","tid":1865913,"uid":8968,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-06T12:21:07.000Z","msg":"講返少少背景, 平時同佢都有講開咸濕笑話<br />\n佢今日係咁話自己口罩又買唔到, 酒精搓手液又買唔到<br />\n咪諗住講個咸濕笑話 「我有好多酒&quot;精&quot; 搓手液喎, 你想要我多多都有<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />」 (已經特登重音左)<br />\n點知佢突然好認真咁問我 「係咪真架, 呃我全家肺炎死呀!」<br />\n因為佢咁認真 我一時反應唔切...就話「係呀...早排入左唔少...哈哈」<br />\n佢好興奮咁叫我俾返一打佢...仲叫我聽日俾佢<br />\n<br />\n我岩岩行均幾十間藥房超市<br />\n屌!一枝一樽仔都冇...<br />\n真係酒&quot;精&quot;都整唔到12枝啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唉, 手足們我聽日點交代好?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"475324fe14a920c0a2346c4795f9900fdfb7e56e","tid":1865913,"uid":49336,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-06T12:21:42.000Z","msg":"0/10"},{"pid":"643b003590a880d06c3d5eb2e6e28c013bab6f13","tid":1865913,"uid":38189,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-06T12:21:47.000Z","msg":"樓主今日得閒到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"27120e1889284f773e7b54762b9793e9f1184e12","tid":1865913,"uid":76527,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-06T12:22:43.000Z","msg":"0/10"},{"pid":"8dbaf75beb0dc1c378acd737e74e266cacbab0ab","tid":1865913,"uid":70195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-06T12:24:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c06e702f50fbc453328a176b929ef30ed228cab7","tid":1865913,"uid":8968,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"643b003590a880d06c3d5eb2e6e28c013bab6f13","tid":1865913,"uid":38189,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-06T12:21:47.000Z","msg":"樓主今日得閒到<